{"tid":2014452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"向佐話希望公眾知道暴力唔能夠解決問題","createTime":"2020-05-13T04:51:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T06:19:57.000Z","uid":316,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d0fc0aec167c341064a41c1c32e14d4a386e973f","tid":2014452,"uid":316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T04:51:03.000Z","msg":"去年 11 月 13 日上水發生反修例運動衝突，七旬食環署外判清潔工羅長清「羅伯」，疑被人以磚頭掟中頭命殞。事發 7 個月，有市民發起今日中午在北區大會堂外進行「悼念羅伯」活動。期間正義聯盟創黨主席李偲嫣，及中國星集團主席向華強的長子向佐到場悼念。<br />\n<br />\n向佐受訪時指希望事件可令公眾知道暴力不能解決問題，希望可以停止暴力，「暴力只會令香港繼續沉淪落去」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CAHWOWrJGoC/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCAHWOWrJGoC%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_web_copy_link&d=RJ6DAKdT%2BAkj0rfdhPz9NUcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=0612c339\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCAHWOWrJGoC%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_web_copy_link&h=d85520e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CAHWOWrJGoC/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link</a>"},{"pid":"63dcdde82410ebd6f69402a2db71b022facbda0f","tid":2014452,"uid":134474,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T04:52:13.000Z","msg":"何佐向右，將身體融入呢個節奏"},{"pid":"313df3f811d7f9847e3ef36e99ce1afda007ed6f","tid":2014452,"uid":89931,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T04:52:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CUZ1Y0s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCUZ1Y0s.jpg&h=0a843f02&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ab9a1c04f32d2c0e26f5949becf82f689a996ca","tid":2014452,"uid":2054,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T04:52:30.000Z","msg":"新義安：暴力不能解決問題"},{"pid":"c70aaf82de430befe3dacbbb13e97d9226cc193d","tid":2014452,"uid":196450,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T04:52:51.000Z","msg":"可以解決提出問題既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class